>\n有冇其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擲一次有6個outcome 123456 每個1/6機會<br />\n擲兩次有11個outcome 2 - 12<br />\n用 nCr / nPr (太耐唔記得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )計每個outcome 既prob"},{"pid":"3cf3947ea6ff7f04eda0a13f7fe3c3e77ffe000b","tid":186914,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5QcMK7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5QcMK7.png&h=ea978312&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nB1:<br />\nK 頭兩日既R (.8+.16) 乘 S 頭兩日既R(0.75+0.1875)<br />\n=0.9<br />\n<br />\nB2:<br />\n如果K第二日睇,S就唔可以第二日睇<br />\n0.16 *(0.75+0.0625) <br />\n如果S第二日睇,K就唔可以第二日睇<br />\n0.1875* (0.8+0.04) <br />\n<br />\n加埋 = 0.2875</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思 想問點解k頭兩日既R可以加埋?"},{"pid":"630740b73fadc3b9393173575e5d397fc079d82d","tid":186914,"uid":89741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5QcMK7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5QcMK7.png&h=ea978312&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nB1:<br />\nK 頭兩日既R (.8+.16) 乘 S 頭兩日既R(0.75+0.1875)<br />\n=0.9<br />\n<br />\nB2:<br />\n如果K第二日睇,S就唔可以第二日睇<br />\n0.16 *(0.75+0.0625) <br />\n如果S第二日睇,K就唔可以第二日睇<br />\n0.1875* (0.8+0.04) <br />\n<br />\n加埋 = 0.2875</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思 想問點解k頭兩日既R可以加埋?</blockquote><br />\n因為我是旦一日睇左都count入條題目既criteria<br />\n0.8 係第一日R<br />\n0.16 係 0.2 * 0.8, 即係第一日NR但第二日R"},{"pid":"9ebcf6914df24ee8c2ee1dfecec86ccac2d51cd9","tid":186914,"uid":43160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1- 兩日兩人都冇睇信 = 1-0.2*0.2*0.25*0.25= 0.9</blockquote><br />\n但係可以有一<span style=\"color: red;\">人</span>睇信，計漏左呢part</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n你岩<img src=\"/assets/